{\fs20 A benefit of a basic understanding of motor control theory is that it provides the practitioner with a base of support on which he or she can develop effective skill instruction and practice environments. }
{\fs20 Fig\u173 ?ure\u8239 ?5.1 illustrates the connection between theory and practice by indicating some of the many applications that will be enhanced when a practitioner has knowledge about the variables that influence motor skill performance. To use one of the examples given at the end of the preceding section, if we know }
{\*\cs49\fs20\b0\i why}{\fs20  people can adapt to a variety of situations when they perform a motor skill, we can use this knowledge to develop practice conditions that we can confidently predict will facilitate this adaptation capability. Consider a different example. Suppose you need to help a person reacquire the capability to walk. Knowledge about the motor control mechanisms that underlie human locomotion and the environmental variables that affect it will allow you to \u173 ?
develop more appropriate assessment and intervention strategies, because they will be based on variables that \u173 ?influence locomotion.}
{\fs20 \par }\pard\plain \s10\f4\fs21\ltrpar\ql\fi0\li0\ri0\sb360\sa120\facenter\sl240\slmult0\expnd0\expndtw0\cf0\up0\charscalex100\keepn\caps\b\i0\ul0\strike0\accnone\hyphpar0\lang1033
{\fs21 Motor Control Theory\par }\pard\plain \s11\f5\fs20\ltrpar\qj\fi0\li0\ri0\sb0\sa0\tx240\facenter\sl240\slmult0\expnd0\expndtw0\cf0\up0\charscalex100\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\accnone\hyphpar1\lang1033
{\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2 In the earlier section titled }{\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2 \ldblquote What Is a theory?\rdblquote  you read that a good theory should describe and provide explanations for a large class of observable events. In light of this requirement, what should a good \u173 ?
theory of motor control describe and explain? \u173 ?Researchers generally acknowledge that it should describe and explain how the nervous system \u173 ?
produces coordinated movement such that we are able to successfully perform a variety of motor skills in a variety of environmental contexts. In many respects, the attempt to understand how we produce coordinated movement is similar to wanting to know how a watch, which also involves the precise coordination of many components, keeps time.\par }
\pard\plain \s13\f5\fs20\ltrpar\qj\fi240\li0\ri0\sb0\sa0\tx240\facenter\sl240\slmult0\expnd0\expndtw0\cf0\up0\charscalex100\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\accnone\hyphpar1\lang1033
