{\fs18 Nicolai Bernstein\rquote s classic book }{\*\cs49\fs18\b0\i The Co-ordination and Regulation of Movement}{\fs18  (published in English in 1967) was a compilation of several of his publications. In the chapter titled \ldblquote Some emergent problems in the regulation of motor acts\rdblquote  (originally published in Russian in 1957), Bernstein discussed the degrees of freedom problem that the motor control system must overcome in order to produce well-coordinated movement. In this discussion (p. 126f\u8201 ?
