{\*\cs62\fs18\b\i\expnd0\expndtw0\cf0\outl0 Motor program theory.}{\fs18 \u8194\'20Gait is controlled by one generalized motor program when walking gait is observed (3\'d06 km/hr) and by a different generalized motor program when the running gait is observed (8\'d012 km/hr).}
{\fs18 \par }\pard\plain \s38\f5\fs18\ltrpar\qj\fi0\li0\ri0\sb220\sa0\tx240\facenter\sl220\slmult0\expnd0\expndtw0\cf0\up0\charscalex100\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\accnone\hyphpar1\lang1033
